text_en:
&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;DIOR
IS DELIGHTED TO ANNOUNCE THE PRESENTATION OF THE EXHIBITION &quot;LADY DIOR AS
SEEN BY&quot;, INCLUDING INTERPRETATIONS OF THE LADY DIOR BAG BY RENOWNED
ARTISTS, FROM 8TH DECEMBER 2018 TO 20TH JANUARY 2019&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;IN
1995 THE LADY DIOR WAS BORN. UPON ITS CREATION IT WAS PRESENTED BY THE FIRST
LADY OF FRANCE AS A GIFT TO DIANA, PRINCESS OF WALES WHO HAD COME TO OPEN THE
CÉZANNE EXHIBITION IN PARIS. THE PRINCESS TOOK IT EVERYWHERE WITH HER. AND THUS
THE LEGEND OF THE LADY DIOR BEGAN.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;ITS
TOPSTITCHED CANNAGE PATTERN, ITS GOLDEN RINGS CONNECTING THE RECTANGULAR BODY
TO THE ARCHING HANDLES, AND ITS DANGLING GOLD LETTERS—IN TRIBUTE TO CHRISTIAN
DIOR’S LOVE OF LUCKY CHARMS—HAVE MADE IT AN ICONIC ACCESSORY OVER THE PAST TWO
DECADES. THE LADY DIOR HAS INSPIRED SOME OF THE GREATEST ARTISTS WORKING TODAY,
TO PRESENT THEIR WORK IN THEIR OWN UNIQUE WAY, AND TO REINTERPRET THE HOUSE’S
ICONIC HANDBAG.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;THE
VERY FOUNDATION OF THE HOUSE OF DIOR’S CORE IDENTITY, THIS LOVE OF ART TODAY
FUELS A VIBRANT DIALOGUE BETWEEN THE DIOR ICON THAT IS THE LADY DIOR AND THE
WORKS OF SOME OF THE MOST TALENTED ARTISTS WORKING TODAY. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;FROM
8TH DECEMBER 2018 TO 20ST JANUARY 2019&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;1st
FLOOR ICONLUXE, ICONSIAM&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

