&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Let’s join #SOOKSANOOK fun activities for kids in Thai style at SOOKSIAM&amp;nbsp; ICONSIAM on Nation Children’s Day&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

text_cn:
