&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 14pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Cordia New&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;A warm welcome to the Thai New Year Festival with The ICONIC
Songkran Festival 2023 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 14pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Cordia New&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;at ICONSIAM&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 14pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Cordia New&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;, excitingly
transforming every inch of ICONSIAM to pass on the precious Thai tradition of
“Songkran Day – The Thai New Year”.&amp;nbsp;
“Water” is used as a medium to portray meaningful relationships and
represents respect, leading to traditions including sprinkling water on Buddha
statues, pouring water on the hands of respected elders, and splashing water to
bring smiles of joy.&amp;nbsp; This year, ICONSIAM
has prepared countless activities for everyone to enjoy every aspect of the refreshing
Songkran Festival, from 11&lt;sup&gt;th&lt;/sup&gt; – 17&lt;sup&gt;th&lt;/sup&gt; April 2023.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;HelveticaNeue-Light, Helvetica Neue Light, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida Grande, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18.6667px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;HelveticaNeue-Light, Helvetica Neue Light, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida Grande, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18.6667px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Water Splash with The Giant Water Tunnel all day long&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Cordia New&amp;quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:
minor-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;One of the highlights of the Songkran Festival at the ICONSIAM is the Giant Water Tunnel at the River Park, for everyone to enjoy the coolness all day long. There is another creative event&amp;nbsp; by ICONSIAM in collaboration with a coffee shop of bringing 100 kilograms of recylced coffee beans into the water tank!&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 24.5333px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 24.5333px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Roboto, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif&quot;&gt;Join the 2023 ICONIC Songkran Festival, b&lt;/font&gt;loom&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 24.5333px;&quot;&gt; the happiness, experience the Thai style enjoyment, and welcome the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 24.5333px;&quot;&gt;Thai &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 24.5333px;&quot;&gt;New Year by the Chao Phraya Riverside&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://iconsiam-s3-prod.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/assets/LGAJQ2Q0TP4OV_SONGKRAN_23_ENG%201040x1040px-01_920x920.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 21.3333px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Showcasing the Thai culture to the World with the Miss Songkran Parade&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Cordia New&amp;quot;,sans-serif;
mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:
minor-bidi&quot;&gt;On 11th April, a parade lead by Yaya Urassaya - who will transform into the beautiful &quot;Kimita Devi&quot;, dressed in a delicate Thai costume and wear ancient Thai accessories worth more than 100 million baht.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Cordia New&amp;quot;,sans-serif;
mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:
minor-bidi&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18.6667px;&quot;&gt;And on 13th April, another Miss Songkran parade lead by Amanada Chalisa, dressed in a costume representing the queen from the Sukhothai era, decorated with the priceless antique gold jewelry - the &quot;Thanim Pim Pa Phon&quot;, at the River Park on G Floor.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://iconsiam-s3-prod.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/assets/LGAJRBBZ7L0ID_SONGKRAN_23_ENG%201040x1040px-02_920x920.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 1rem;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Cordia New&amp;quot;,sans-serif;
mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:
minor-bidi&quot;&gt;Dance along with the Thai music artists at mini concerts&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; min-height: 15px;&quot;&gt;Experience the brand-new water-splashing activity at the River Park on the G floor, and immerse yourself in the mini-concerts held by well-known Thai artists. Starts at 7:00 p.m. every day and continues for 7 consecutive days!&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;April 11, 2023 - NEW COUNTRY&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; min-height: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;April 12, 2023 - PROXIE&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; min-height: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;April 13, 2023 - THREE MAN DOWN&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; min-height: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;April 14, 2023 - The singers of the Thai variety show &quot;Best Song Contest&quot;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; min-height: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;April 15, 2023 - TILLY BIRDS&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; min-height: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;April 16, 2023 - RSF&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; min-height: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;April 17, 2023 - ATLAS&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://iconsiam-s3-prod.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/assets/LGAJS3DTQR2M0_SONGKRAN_23_ENG%201040x1040px_920x920.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 1rem;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Cordia New&amp;quot;,sans-serif;
mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:
minor-bidi&quot;&gt;New Year Praying at the Charo Phraya Riverside&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Cordia New&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: -18pt; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Enhance the auspiciousness and welcome the Thai New Year by sprinkling some water on the Pollen Buddha Statue (“Gaysorn Dok Mai”), an ancient Buddha statue from the reign of King Rama 5 of over 100 years old from Ubon Ratchathani Province at Ratsada Hall, 1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;sup style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Cordia New&amp;quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: -18pt; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;st&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Cordia New&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: -18pt; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; Floor.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Cordia New&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: -18pt; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Big Promotion for Shopping Spree during Songkran Festival&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;ICONSIAM splashes the happiness to all our customers by celebrating the 2023 ICONIC Songkran Festival.&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-family: Roboto, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem;&quot;&gt;Enjoy shopping with a joyful promotion during Songkran Redeem prizes worth more than 2.2 million baht between April 7, 2023 – May 6, 2023 for VIZ members registered with ONESIAM SuperApp, just purchase goods and services in ICONSIAM, including Siam Takashimaya, in accordance with Conditions, can redeem VIZ COIN worth up to 400 baht!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-family: Roboto, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem;&quot;&gt;From April 13, 2023 – April 17, 2023, only 5 days for VIZ members with ONESIAM SuperApp, complete the purchase according to the conditions, redeem Lotus&#039;s Privé Cash Coupon and VIZ COIN worth up to 800 baht.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: Gotham, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Get your Thai costumes ready!&amp;nbsp; ICONSIAM is ready to welcome you with the freshness of water and joy.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://iconsiam-s3-prod.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/assets/LGAICPTSZ710W_LFJ7M9BQY9YVT_ICONSIAM-songkran-2023-2.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://iconsiam-s3-prod.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/assets/LGAICYP2CM1RN_LFJ7N0J9GP9QF_ICONSIAM-songkran-2023-1.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;

text_th:
ห้ามพลาดกับ &lt;strong&gt;BTS EXHIBITION: PROOF&lt;/strong&gt; นิทรรศการ สุดอลังการ เพื่อเป็นการเฉลิมฉลองครบ 10 &amp;nbsp;ปี ของวง BTS ครั้งแรกในประเทศไทย และเป็นประเทศแรก ในเอเชียตะวันออกเฉียงใต้ที่มีการจัดนิทรรศการนี้ขึ้นอย่างยิ่งใหญ่ เพื่อให้เหล่าอาร์มี่ในไทย ได้ร่วมเฉลิมฉลองทุกช่วงเวลาในประวัติศาสตร์ของ BTS&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
คุณจะได้พบกับนิทรรศการระดับโลกแบบเอ็กซ์คลูซีฟที่บอกเล่าเรื่องราวของศิลปินวง BTS ทั้ง 7 คน ได้แก่ RM, Jin, SUGA, J-Hope, Jimin, V และ Jungkook ตั้งแต่ก่อนที่พวกเขาจะกลายมาเป็นหนึ่งในวงดนตรีที่โด่งดังที่สุดของโลกเช่นทุก วันนี้ ผ่านภาพถ่าย วิดีโอ และโซนจัดแสดงเสมือนจริง&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
อีกหนึ่งไฮไลต์ที่พลาดไม่ได้ คือ โซนของที่ระลึก โดยผู้เข้าชมสามารถเลือกซื้อสินค้าลิมิเต็ด อิดิชั่น ของวง BTS และของที่ระลึกจากงานแสดงที่ประเทศไทย สุดเอ็กซ์คลูซีฟ อาทิ เซตโปสการ์ด BTS, เซตโปสเตอร์ BTS รวมถึงกระเป๋าที่ออกแบบพิเศษ&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
ตั้งแต่ 3 ส.ค. - 3 ก.ย. 66&lt;br /&gt;
เวลา 10.30 - 22.00 น. (เข้าชมรอบละ 60 นาที)&lt;br /&gt;
ณ ICON Art &amp;amp; Culture Space ชั้น 8 ไอคอนสยาม&lt;br /&gt;
บัตรราคา 880 บาท รอบวันธรรมดา และราคา 1,080 บาท รอบวันเสาร์-อาทิตย์ และวันหยุดนักขัตฤกษ์&lt;br /&gt;
ซื้อบัตรเข้าชมได้ที่ &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.ticketmelon.com&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;ticketmelon.com&lt;/a&gt;

text_en:
&lt;meta charset=&quot;utf-8&quot; /&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;Don&amp;rsquo;t miss out! The BTS EXHIBITION: PROOF &amp;ndash; a grand exhibition to celebrate BTS&amp;rsquo;s 10th debut anniversary for the very first time in Thailand.&amp;nbsp; Thailand is the first country in Southeast Asia to hold a grand exhibition for Thai ARMY to celebrate the precious moment in the history of BTS.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;Get ready to exclusively experience a world class exhibition that tells the story of all 7 members of BTS; RM, Jin, SUGA, J-Hope, Jimin, V, and Jungkook, from the very beginning before becoming one of the world&amp;rsquo;s most famous boyband today through photos, videos, and a virtual exhibition zone.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;Another highlight not to be missed is the merchandise zone, where visitors can enjoy a selection of BTS&amp;#39;s limited-edition official goods from events in Thailand such as BTS postcard collections, poster sets, as well as exclusively designed bags.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;From 3rd Aug to 3rd Sep 2023&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;From 10.30a.m. to 10.00p.m. (60 minutes per round)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;At ICON Art &amp;amp; Culture Space on the 8th Floor of ICONSIAM&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;Ticket prices are at THB 880 on weekdays and THB 1,080 on weekends and public holidays.&lt;/p&gt;
Tickets are available for purchase at &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.ticketmelon.com&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;ticketmelon.com&lt;/a&gt;

text_cn:
&lt;meta charset=&quot;utf-8&quot; /&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;千万别错过盛大的BTS EXHIBITION：PROOF展览！该展览首次在泰国举办，欢庆BTS防弹少年团出道10周年。泰国是东南亚首个举办如此盛大展览的国家，让泰国的ARMY们能够一起回顾BTS过去十年的历史性时刻。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;这是一个世界级展览，通过照片、影片和虚拟展览区讲述BTS七位成员：RM金南俊、Jin金硕珍、SUGA闵玧其、J-Hope、Jimin朴智旻、V金泰亨和Jung Kook田柾国在成为世界顶级知名男团之一前的故事。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;该展另一个不容错过的亮点是纪念品区。参观者可以在此处购买到BTS限量版的周边商品和演唱会泰国场的产品。其中包括了一些独特商品，如：BTS明信片套装、BTS海报套装以及独家设计的包包。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;展出日期：2023年8月3日至9月3日&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;营业时间：上午10:30 &amp;ndash; 晚上10:00（每轮参观时间为60分钟）&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;展出场地：暹罗天地ICONSIAM 8楼，ICON Art &amp;amp; Culture Space&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;票价：平日票价为880泰铢；周末及公共假期票价为1,080泰铢&lt;/p&gt;
