Welcome to the festival for coffee lovers, with over 50 renowned coffee shops to offer varieties of coffee blend. Immerse yourself in the world of specialty coffee with over a hundred menu selections, including championship-grade barista-brewed coffees bean and non- caffeine options, waiting to serve with a delightful experience for everyone.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
