text_en:
ICONSIAM is delighted to unveil a special gift for everyone with &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;Da Vinci Alive Bangkok,&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt; the world&amp;#39;s most comprehensive immersive experience dedicated to one of history&amp;#39;s greatest minds. This exhibition will come to life from March 15 to July 31, 2024, at the Attraction Hall, 6th floor, ICONSIAM, marking its first-ever debut in Thailand and is considered the most complete in Asia.&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
Every second of your journey into the world of &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;Da Vinci Alive Bangkok&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt; will transport you back 570 years to explore the legacy of Leonardo da Vinci, the Italian genius who mastered various disciplines. As an artist, sculptor, musician, and also a scientist, inventor, mathematician, engineer, and architect, Leonardo da Vinci&amp;#39;s contributions have been unparalleled, inspiring artists and people across the globe immensely.&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
The exhibition, a highlight of impressive immersion, is divided into two main sections. The first zone, the Experience Zone, takes you on a journey into the world of Leonardo da Vinci, brought to life through tangible and photographable installations enriched with detailed insights for learning. The second zone, the Immersive Show, offers a digital art exhibition that immerses you in the virtual world of Leonardo da Vinci.&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;First time ever in Asia that the secret will be revealed&lt;/strong&gt;, a special surprise of &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;Da Vinci Alive Bangkok&amp;quot; &lt;/strong&gt;is your opportunity to uncover the mysteries behind the world-famous Mona Lisa painting. Celebrate the captivating art stories of the Italian Renaissance, the most significant era in art history, spanning from the 14th to the 17th century, through an astonishing digital gallery.&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
Get ready to enjoy the immersive digital art exhibition at ICONSIAM&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Da Vinci Alive Bangkok&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Show Date: March 15, 2024 &amp;ndash; July 31, 2024&lt;br /&gt;
Location: Attraction Hall, 6th floor, ICONSIAM&lt;br /&gt;
Opening hours: 10:30 AM - 9:00 PM.&lt;br /&gt;
Ticket fee
