The guided tours can be reserved in advance at Ticketmelon.com.&amp;nbsp; The order will be processed once the booking and the payment has been made.&amp;nbsp; Tickets will be sent as QR codes via email, but can also be accessed on Ticketmelon&amp;rsquo;s website and official application.&amp;nbsp; Please present your QR code to the staff once you have arrived at the venue on the reserved date, and it is recommended that you arrive at the venue 30 minutes before the starting time.&lt;br /&gt;
