&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;踏入《招魂宇宙巡演》，迎接即将到来的恐怖之旅。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXenX4KG6AtoBiNPfCV1rFX7ixyMHWqwOEWFMyNFdiUB88T-tL4HHPbohZWo5dFPEe_LF0FsssWlsfFb1ezAwjHysIQCI5eR3DD8WCQz8vcUUVCeBWZfEihod9Bd_xF-A6GCtlQQsa1Wb7cuaZMzev8GsGuvnN5vXjqGVop6L8D6GuotnOpVT8s?key=1Kj6qwScZVaxqtu7v-EvKg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

