text_en:
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;#Highlights of the ICONIC CRAFT COFFEE EXPO 2024 at ICONSIAM&lt;br /&gt;
The grandest coffee journey of the year, opening up a delightful world of coffee that will make you fall in love even more.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://iconsiam-s3-prod.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/assets/1724907329M.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Over 1,000 Menus from 230 renowned coffee brands: Spread across more than 4,000 square meters, savor the deliciousness of drinks crafted by expert baristas.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;For the first time ever, the Thailand Iconic Coffee &amp; Creativity Championship 2024 (TICC) offers a grand prize of 100,000 baht. Witness the competition judged by world-class baristas and discover the next coffee champion.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Exclusive free workshops hosted by world-renowned barista judge, Kat Chanya Tharathikunach. Learn from the best in the industry.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Enjoy the Atmosphere with Global Coffee Experts: Surround yourself with ICONIC PERSON coffee experts from around the world who will be on-site to share their insider tips.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Explore a wide range of coffee products including global coffee brands, Thai and international coffee beans, GI coffee beans, coffee machines, and accessories.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Discover a diverse selection of coffee shops, from local cafes to celebrity-owned coffee houses, along with delectable pastries and bakery items. &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;Enjoy exclusive promotions with the &quot;ICONIC Craft Coffee Journey. Collect stamps with the Journey Passport and enjoy exclusive rewards. Every purchase, from coffee beans to coffee machines, earns you stamps to win amazing prizes.&lt;/p&gt;

