&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;Similar to how diamonds attain their luster through time and pressure, SEVENTEEN has devoted an immense amount of effort to crystallize a single moment of brilliance on stage.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;Prior to showcasing their flawlessly timed performance that unites 13 members into a harmonious whole, SEVENTEEN underwent a meticulous polishing process that could only be described as top-notch teamwork in action.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;We invite you to experience the emotions of the concert and the messages conveyed by the members during this exhibition, as we follow the trails of SEVENTEEN&#039;s unwavering dedication and intensive practice.&lt;/p&gt;

