text_en:
This year, the festive season at ICONSIAM shines brighter than ever with the spectacular &lt;strong&gt;ICONSIAM BANGKOK ILLUMINATION 2024 X ROBBi&lt;/strong&gt;,&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://iconsiam-s3-prod.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/assets/1731405671W.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;A Magnificent 20-Meter Christmas Tree&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Adorned with &lt;strong&gt;Snowflake-inspired ornaments&lt;/strong&gt; crafted from &lt;em&gt;&amp;ldquo;krieb glass&amp;rdquo;&lt;/em&gt; (crackle glass), the design draws inspiration from the Hiranyikarn flower&amp;mdash;a Thai blossom symbolizing prosperity, wealth, abundance, and success. This uniquely stunning creation even moves in rhythm with enchanting melodies, offering a one-of-a-kind visual experience.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://iconsiam-s3-prod.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/assets/1731405705K.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;ROBBi &amp;ndash; The World&amp;rsquo;s Largest ROBBi&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
For the first time in Thailand and Southeast Asia, meet &lt;strong&gt;ROBBi&lt;/strong&gt;, an awe-inspiring metallic art toy as tall as ICONSIAM itself! Designed with shimmering gold and silver hues that reflect dazzling lights, ROBBi appears to float in the air, surrounded by oversized Hiranyikarn blossoms. With a relaxed and playful pose, ROBBi invites you to enjoy the festive vibes and breathtaking views of the Chao Phraya River.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://iconsiam-s3-prod.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/assets/1731405742D.jpg&quot; /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Special Performances: The Thai-conic Christmas Symphony&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Don&amp;rsquo;t miss the mesmerizing light show where the Christmas tree lights up and moves in harmony with music. This symphony blends the melodious charm of traditional Thai instruments with classical sounds, composed and arranged by Dr. Narong Prangcharoen, the first Thai recipient of the prestigious &lt;strong&gt;Charles Ives Fellowship&lt;/strong&gt; from the American Academy of Arts and Letters.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Performance Times&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;br /&gt;
Three shows daily at &lt;strong&gt;6:50 PM, 7:50 PM, and 8:50 PM&lt;/strong&gt; from &lt;strong&gt;1 November to 25 December 2024&lt;/strong&gt;, spreading happiness and prosperity throughout this festive season.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://iconsiam-s3-prod.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/assets/1731409014P.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;ROBBi Pop-Up Store&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Explore a limited-edition collection of ROBBi art pieces, available for the first time in Southeast Asia. Discover exclusive designs and take home a piece of this magical celebration.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
ICONSIAM is ready to light up your holiday season&amp;mdash;step into a world of festive joy and artistic marvels today!&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;ICONSIAM BANGKOK ILLUMINATION 2024 X ROBBi&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
Today - December 25,2024&lt;br /&gt;
River Park, ICONSIAM&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
