text_en:
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://iconsiam-s3-prod.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/assets/1735533039K.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
 &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The ultimate countdown experience awaits at ICONSIAM—your one and only destination for the most spectacular New Year’s celebration! Featuring an unmatched lineup of artists, ICONSIAM promises the best, most exciting performances to ring in the new year.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For those celebrating from home, immerse yourself in the electrifying atmosphere of this Global Countdown Destination. Don’t miss the LIVE broadcast, showcasing exclusive world-class performances by iconic international and Thai artists, brought together for an unforgettable night—only at ICONSIAM.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Tune in to LIVE on FACEBOOK and YOUTUBE ICONSIAM on December 31, 2024, starting at 5:30 PM.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://iconsiam-s3-prod.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/assets/1735533079O.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
ICONSIAM proudly presents the grand event, Amazing Thailand Countdown 2025, reaffirming its status as a true Global Countdown Destination. Join us for a world-class celebration spanning three consecutive days!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;meta charset=&quot;utf-8&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;GLOBAL THAI-CONIC FIREWORKS CELEBRATION&lt;/strong&gt;                                                                             &lt;br /&gt;
The Amazing Thailand Countdown 2025 invites everyone to usher in the New Year with joy through Thailand’s longest eco-friendly fireworks display along the Chao Phraya River. This 1,400-meter display, visible over a 5-kilometer radius, is directed by world-renowned Japanese pyrotechnician “Oguchi Yoshimasa.” Inspired by the theme “Celebrating the Everlasting Legacy of Siam,” the display reflects the vibrant beauty of Thailand&#039;s heritage and wisdom.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://iconsiam-s3-prod.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/assets/1731583614G.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;GLOBAL THAI-CONIC CAPTIVATING HERO&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
This year’s Amazing Thailand Countdown 2025 stage at ICONSIAM promises a multi-dimensional entertainment experience. With the exciting confirmation that Lisa (Lalisa Manobal), a world-renowned rapper, singer, dancer and style icon will perform an exclusive show, this celebration is truly a gift for everyone.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://iconsiam-s3-prod.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/assets/1731583641M.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;GLOBAL THAI-CONIC ENTERTAINMENT SHOWCASE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
ICONSIAM brings non-stop entertainment from top artists over three full days, with special highlights including Zee Nunew, Milli, BUS, Proxie, Nont Tanont, PP-Billkin, Atlas, 4EVE, Jeff Satur, Peck Palitchoke, Kongthap Peak, the band Perses, Nok KPN (Thailand’s first solo senior vocalist world champion), the cast of PIT BABE The Series, and global Chinese superstar Wei Zheming.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://iconsiam-s3-prod.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/assets/1732076125T.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
The only place to celebrate this New Year’s Eve is ICONSIAM! The Amazing Thailand Countdown 2025 is set to deliver surprises in every dimension, solidifying its place as a true Global Countdown Destination.&lt;br /&gt;
 
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ICONSIAM invites you to the Magnificent Amazing Thailand Countdown 2025&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Join us for the most anticipated celebration of the year by the Chao Phraya River. Immerse yourself in the magic of the New Year with &lt;strong&gt;3 Easy Steps&lt;/strong&gt; to secure your spot at this iconic world-class event, happening from &lt;strong&gt;29–31 December 2024&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;For more information about tickets &gt;&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://bit.ly/3Dd3POC&quot;&gt;https://bit.ly/3Dd3POC&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://iconsiam-s3-prod.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/assets/1734420680R.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://iconsiam-s3-prod.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/assets/1734420702V.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://iconsiam-s3-prod.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/assets/1734420717H.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

text_cn:
&lt;meta charset=&quot;utf-8&quot; /&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://iconsiam-s3-prod.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/assets/1735533145O.jpg&quot; /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
ICONSIAM 为您带来终极倒计时体验&amp;mdash;&amp;mdash;体验无比壮观的迎接新年系列庆祝活动的唯一之选！ICONSIAM 拥有无与伦比的艺术家阵容，承诺以最精彩、最激动人心的表演迎接新年。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;对于居家庆祝的人来说，也可以一起沉浸在这个全球级别跨年倒计时目的地令人振奋的氛围中。锁定线上同步直播，欣赏标志性的国际和泰国艺术家带来的的独家表演，让我们汇聚在一起度过一个难忘的夜晚&amp;mdash;&amp;mdash;就在 ICONSIAM。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;2024 年 12 月 31 日下午 5:30 开始，在 FACEBOOK 和 YOUTUBE ICONSIAM 官方账户上收看直播。&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://iconsiam-s3-prod.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/assets/1735533174C.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
ICONSIAM 无比自豪地呈现盛大的 Amazing Thailand Countdown 2025 庆祝活动，重申其作为全球级别跨年目的地的地位。欢迎大家加入这为期三天的世界级庆典！&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;标志性巨型烟花秀&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Amazing Thailand Countdown 2025 邀请大家在泰国最长的环保烟花表演中，喜迎新年。这场长达 1,400 米的烟花表演将在湄南河畔上演，可视范围超过 5 公里，由世界著名的日本烟花导演 &amp;ldquo;Oguchi Yoshimasa&amp;rdquo; 亲自操刀，以&amp;ldquo;庆祝暹罗的永恒遗产&amp;rdquo;为主题，展现泰国遗产和智慧的多彩之美。&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://iconsiam-s3-prod.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/assets/1731583614G.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;LISA 倾情献演，开启全球瞩目的跨年倒计时&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
今年 Amazing Thailand Countdown 2025 的舞台将在 ICONSIAM 呈现多维度的氛围效果，更邀请到&amp;ldquo;Lalisa Manoban&amp;rdquo;带来独家表演，给所有观众带来特别的观赏体验。&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://iconsiam-s3-prod.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/assets/1731583641M.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;史诗般的三天娱乐盛宴&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
