text_en:
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;DINOLAB BANGKOK 2025 Jurassic Domination presents an exciting new experience in one of the most advanced science labs ever created! Here, you&amp;#39;ll witness dinosaurs coming back to life through cutting-edge animatronic technology, bringing these ancient creatures to life with lifelike movements like never before!&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;Step into the world filled with mystery and fun learning, as you explore the science behind these amazing technologies that have brought dinosaurs back to our time. It&amp;#39;s not just an adventure&amp;mdash;it&amp;#39;s a journey into the future of science and innovation. Don&amp;#39;t miss the chance to be part of this extraordinary journey through time!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;meta charset=&quot;utf-8&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Event Highlights&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li aria-level=&quot;1&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;
	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;Dino Train Ride Experience: Board a simulated train through a destroyed laboratory marked by dinosaur traces.&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li aria-level=&quot;1&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;
	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;Dinosaur Exhibition: Marvel at colossal dinosaur models.&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li aria-level=&quot;1&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;
	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;Dinosaur Riding: Ride life-sized, realistic, and friendly dinosaurs for a close-up experience.&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li aria-level=&quot;1&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;
	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;Dinosaur Egg Hatching: Interact with realistic dinosaur hatchlings and learn how to care for them.&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;Fossil Digging Area: Use simulated tools to excavate dinosaur fossils.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Zones&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li aria-level=&quot;1&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;
	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;The Boy&amp;rsquo;s Room: A secret base leading to the laboratory, symbolizing the dream of reviving dinosaurs.&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li aria-level=&quot;1&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;
	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;The Lab: Embark on a journey via a simulated train to explore a destroyed laboratory and unlock its mysteries.&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li aria-level=&quot;1&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;
	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;DNA Restoration Center: Learn about DNA reconstruction and engage in educational activities suitable for all ages.&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li aria-level=&quot;1&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;
	&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;Dino Paradise: Enjoy life-sized dinosaurs in a natural, photogenic setting, perfect for families.&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;Additionally, there will be a merchandise area featuring over 1,000 exclusive items available only in Thailand.&lt;br /&gt;
